        {
            "title": "泰國曼谷2米巨蜥吞食棄嬰  吃剩頭和上身 目擊居民：嚇到嘔",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/74b45859fd692f92893ea4b47be9c48d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051605545798637.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>泰國驚傳恐怖悲劇，一條約2米長的巨型蜥蜴周四在首都曼谷近郊欖府（Samut Prakan）被發現吞食一名新生嬰兒，場面血腥，震驚當地居民。\n\n</p>\n<p>事發於一片雜草叢生的荒地，當地居民驚見巨蜥口中叼着一具嬰兒屍體奔走，嚇得立即報警求助。當地救援人員及動物控制隊迅速趕到現場，發現該條巨蜥正躲藏於濃密草叢之中，口中仍咬着嬰兒下半身殘骸，當人員試圖捕捉時，牠迅速逃入一堵水泥圍牆下。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251215/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一條約2米長的巨型蜥蜴周四在首都曼谷近郊欖府被發現吞食一名新生嬰兒，人員到垾調查。影片畫面截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/904bac16616c759709835eafd51e2da2/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-15_at_9_21_23_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一條約2米長的巨型蜥蜴周四在首都曼谷近郊欖府被發現吞食一名新生嬰兒，人員到垾調查。影片畫面截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251216/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c3619bedd1cdfacb447b93e54a8527d9/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-15_at_9_21_47_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251217/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c86b2fc79759f4b48f6a7a0f1c2e5c30/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-15_at_9_21_53_PM_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251218/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8442dd1f643967b7f2c74bd4aee0110f/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-15_at_9_21_56_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251219/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a16f276c13046e75587df6033bfb954/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-15_at_9_22_34_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251220/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c978645753cf7a17d61ea59a0367672e/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-15_at_9_22_46_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>目擊畫面顯示，這條彷彿「哥斯拉」般的巨型爬蟲潛伏在水澤一隅，大啖嬰兒屍體，而不遠處則發現嬰兒的頭部與軀幹。\n\n</p>\n<p>救援義工柴布米（Chaiwat Boonmee）透露，該巨蜥曾把屍體拖至附近屋下，增加屍體回收的難度。他表示，嬰兒其後被送往法醫研究所進行屍檢，以查明確切死因。目前未知巨蜥開始啃食嬰兒時，嬰兒是否已死去。\n\n</p>\n<p>報案的居民指出，最初以為巨蜥啃食的是一條魚，但靠近一看竟發現是嬰兒的遺體，驚恐萬分。他說：「我一開始還以為牠嘴裡叼的是魚，但走近一看才發現竟是一具嬰兒屍體，當場嘔心。」\n\n</p>\n<p>初步調查顯示，該名嬰兒應在兩日前出生，極可能是遭棄置荒野後被野生巨蜥發現並吞噬。當局現正調查死者身份及父母下落，涉案者或將面臨遺棄罪指控。\n\n</p>\n<p>根據泰國法律，棄養9歲以下兒童屬刑事罪，最高可判3年監禁或罰款約135英鎊（約5,300泰銖），或兩者兼施。\n\n</p>\n<p>雖然巨蜥在東南亞地區常見，平日以魚類、小蛇及垃圾為食，甚少主動攻擊人類，但類似事件並非首次發生。2020年，泰國南部洛坤府（Nakhon Si Thammarat）亦曾有一名被棄嬰兒被巨蜥啃食，當時由孩童於池塘邊發現裝有遺體的黑膠袋，震驚社會。警方表示，嬰兒的親生父母刻意棄嬰在池塘邊，導致無辜的孩子成為巨蜥的腹中物。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
